headline: Trimble Inc. (TRMB) Taps Martin Equipment as Trimble Technology Outlet
summary: Trimble Inc. (NASDAQ:TRMB) is one of the best lidar stocks to buy right now. On September 9, the company confirmed the addition of Martin Equipment as a new member of the Trimble Technology outlet. The strategic deal opens the door for Martin Equipment to sell Trimble grade control site positioning systems and correction services technology […]
